[Ontology Constraints (约束)]:
1. 实体类别(Entity)仅限: [Device, Component, Phenomenon, Fault_Cause, Solution, Model_Type, Metric, Alg_Issue, Tuning_Strategy]。
2. 关系类别(Relation)仅限: [HAS_PART, SHOWS_ABNORM, INDICATES, REQUIRES, EVALUATED_BY, EXHIBITS, MITIGATED_BY]。

